title: Taras Schevchenko - Poems.ukr.eng.fre.ger.pdf
description:
This collection of poems was published in 1961 in Munich due to the efforts of Ukrainian diaspora.

If you do not know who Shevchenko was read this http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Taras_Shevchenko

"He was a son of a serf and became the colossus of human spirit."

There are the originals of the poems and translations into English and into French and/or German.

Downloaded from diasporiana(dot)org(dot)ua

Enjoy!
